# Redirect www to non-www
https://www.jacobmacdonnell.com/* https://jacobmacdonnell.com/:splat 301!
https://www.jacobmacdonnell.ca/* https://jacobmacdonnell.com/:splat 301!

# Redirect .ca to .com
https://jacobmacdonnell.ca/* https://jacobmacdonnell.com/:splat 301!

# Force HTTPS (Netlify does this by default, but just in case)
http://jacobmacdonnell.com/* https://jacobmacdonnell.com/:splat 301!
http://jacobmacdonnell.ca/* https://jacobmacdonnell.com/:splat 301!
http://www.jacobmacdonnell.com/* https://jacobmacdonnell.com/:splat 301!
http://www.jacobmacdonnell.ca/* https://jacobmacdonnell.com/:splat 301!